0produced%20in%20India%20under%20the%20'Make%20in%20India'%20programme.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fadani-defence-and-aerospace-delivers-first-batch-of-prahar-guns-to-indian-army-11278937%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fadani-defence-and-aerospace-delivers-first-batch-of-prahar-guns-to-indian-army-11278937%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fadani-defence-and-aerospace-delivers-first-batch-of-prahar-guns-to-indian-army-11278937%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20moved%20from%20Texas%20to%20Italy%20to%20retire.%20I'm%20saving%20over%20%2420%2C000%20a%20year%20on%20healthcare%2C%20and%20life%20is%20cheaper%20and%20calmer%20overall.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20standing%20outside%20of%20a%20building%20in%20Italy.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6aa7b8e44c01630d317a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBrad%20Allan%20decided%20to%20retire%20in%20Italy%20instead%20of%20the%20US.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Brad%20Allan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBrad%20Allan%20and%20his%20wife%20moved%20to%20Montepulciano%2C%20Italy%2C%20to%20live%20out%20their%20retirement%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EItaly's%20low-cost%20healthcare%20was%20a%20big%20draw%20coming%20from%20the%20US.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAllan%20said%20having%20a%20home%20base%20in%20Italy%20has%20made%20traveling%20throughout%20Europe%20easier%20and%20cheaper.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Brad%20Allan%2C%20an%20American%20who%20relocated%20from%20Austin%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20Olivia%2C%20to%20Montepulciano%2C%20Italy%2C%20to%20retire.%20Allan%2C%2060%2C%20now%20gives%20advice%20to%20other%20expats%20in%20Italy%20through%20his%20YouTube%20channel%2C%20BradsWorld.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20US%2C%20I%20owned%20a%20chain%20of%20furniture%20stores%20and%20dabbled%20in%20investing%20in%20multifamily%20real%20estate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20me%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-sold-everything-retired-in-europe-albania-pros-cons-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eretiring%20in%20Europe%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20about%20being%20able%20to%20keep%20up%20the%20lifestyle%20that%20I%20had%20when%20I%20was%20running%20my%20stores%20and%20owning%20multifamily%20and%20actively%20working%20in%20the%20US.%20Without%20being%20clich%C3%A9%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20be%20able%20to%20lead%20a%20Champagne%20life%20on%20a%20beer%20budget%3B%20to%20be%20able%20to%20stretch%20our%20dollars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20look%20online%2C%20it's%20so%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-bought-a-cheap-house-in-italy-sicily-listings-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einexpensive%20to%20buy%20nice%20properties%20in%20Europe%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20can%20remember%20at%20least%2010%20years%20ago%20looking%20at%20real%20estate%20listings%20and%20daydreaming%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleaving-us-for-italy-retire-in-sicily-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eretiring%20in%20Italy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Southern%20France%2C%20or%20Spain.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20big%20travelers%20%E2%80%94%20my%20wife%20and%20I%20were%20lucky%20enough%20to%20be%20able%20to%20take%20three%20or%20four%20international%20trips%20a%20year.%20We%20went%20everywhere%2C%20but%20we%20always%20gravitated%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-region-in-italy-to-visit-from-frequent-traveler-basilicata-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eback%20to%20Southern%20Europe%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20Italy%20was%20always%20on%20the%20radar.%20We%20got%20serious%20about%20it%20just%20before%20COVID.%20We%20took%20a%20six-week%20trip%20in%20the%20fall%20of%202019%2C%20and%20drove%20around%20all%20of%20Italy%20from%20the%20very%20northern%20part%20all%20the%20way%20down%20into%20the%20heel%20of%20the%20boot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224445%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22View%20over%20the%20Tuscan%20countryside%20and%20the%20town%20of%20Montepulciano%20at%20sunset%2C%20Italy%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6b7bfe99557fb1b08a0bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222964%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMontepulciano%2C%20Italy.%3Cp%3Ejenifoto%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20ended%20up%20choosing%20to%20buy%20property%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftuscany-americans-moving-italy-cost-of-living-slow-pace-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESouthern%20Tuscany%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20specifically%20right%20on%20the%20Umbria%20border.%20The%20other%20areas%20are%20nice%2C%20but%20we%20felt%20most%20comfortable%20here%20%E2%80%94%20we%20had%20been%20here%20a%20lot%20and%20knew%20a%20lot%20of%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20moved%20here%20full-time%20in%202023%20and%20love%20it.%20We%20just%20felt%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20natural%20beauty%20here%20is%20otherworldly.%20We've%20found%20the%20people%20to%20be%20very%20friendly%2C%20and%20people%20always%20talk%20about%20%3Cem%3Ela%20dolce%20vita%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20slower%20pace%20of%20life.%20Plus%2C%20we%20really%20like%20wine%2C%20and%20the%20quality%20here%20is%20second%20to%20none.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a361b510-5e1f-4bba-b45f-c6a6570fa2a2%5C%22%3EItaly's%20healthcare%20is%20inexpensive%20compared%20to%20the%20US%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20No.%201%20thing%20to%20know%20is%20that%20in%20general%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-living-in-italy-thankful-for-healthcare-for-daughter-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehealthcare%20in%20Italy%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20very%20inexpensive.%20Even%20if%20you're%20not%20on%20the%20national%20healthcare%20plan%2C%20you%20can%20come%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you're%20retired%2C%20you're%20not%20having%20anybody%20paying%20into%20the%20system%20for%20you.%20So%20we%20paid%202%2C800%20euros%20%5B%3Cem%3Eabout%20%243%2C228%3C%2Fem%3E%5D%20for%20our%20buy-in%20to%20the%20national%20healthcare%20system%20for%20the%20year.%20What%20was%20our%20payment%20for%20one%20month%20in%20the%20US%20pays%20our%20healthcare%20for%20the%20year%2C%20and%20we%20don't%20really%20have%20to%20pay%20for%20anything%20unless%20we%20wanted%20one%20expedited%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20my%20wife%20needed%20an%20MRI%2C%20with%20and%20without%20contrast%2C%20and%20we%20went%20to%20the%20local%20MRI%20private%20clinic%20not%20through%20the%20healthcare%20system.%20I%20believe%20it%20was%20200%20euros%20for%20two%20different%20MRIs.%20I%20had%20to%20get%20an%20X-ray%2C%20and%20it%20was%20%2430.%20A%20doctor's%20visit%20is%2050%20euros%2C%20and%20a%20specialist%20visit%20is%20120%20euros.%20So%20it's%20very%20inexpensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20and%20woman%20taking%20a%20selfie.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6aa7be99557fb1b08a035%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAllan%20and%20his%20wife%2C%20Olivia.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Brad%20Allan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAt%2060%20years%20old%2C%20I'm%20still%20five%20years%20away%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeet-the-americans-on-the-brink-of-losing-health-insurance-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebeing%20able%20to%20get%20Medicare%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20my%20wife's%2015%20years%20away%20from%20that.%20So%20that's%20a%20long%20time%20when%20you're%20unemployed%20%E2%80%94%20as%20you%20are%20when%20you're%20retired%20%E2%80%94%20to%20be%20paying%20%243%2C000%20a%20month%20in%20healthcare%20costs%20in%20the%20US.%20So%20that's%20a%20huge%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20say%2C%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20the%20taxes%20are%20so%20high%20in%20Italy.%20It's%20six%20points%20higher%20than%20the%20top%20line%20in%20the%20US.%26quot%3B%20And%20yes%2C%20the%20scale%20maxes%20out%20much%20lower%20than%20the%20US%2C%20but%20taxes%20aren't%20just%20federal%20income%20tax%3B%20it's%20also%20property%20tax%2C%20and%20I%20consider%20healthcare%20costs%20to%20be%20a%20tax%2C%20especially%20when%20you're%20retired.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20all%20those%20things%20together%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-from-florida-to-italy-cheaper-homes-better-healthcare-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EItaly%20is%20much%20more%20affordable%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20because%20when%20you're%20retired%2C%20you're%20not%20making%20as%20much%20income.%20And%20yeah%2C%20maybe%20we%20paid%20an%20extra%20%245%2C000%20in%20federal%20tax%20here%2C%20but%20we%20saved%20%2420%2C000%20in%20property%20tax%2C%20which%20is%20what%20we%20had%20to%20pay%20in%20Texas.%20And%20we%20saved%20over%20%2420%2C000%20in%20healthcare%20costs.%20That's%20huge%20savings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22843c051b-25d9-4124-88fe-d36134772207%5C%22%3ELiving%20in%20Europe%20is%20calmer%2C%20and%20traveling%20is%20a%20lot%20easier%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENobody%20here%20asks%20you%20what%20you%20do.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20much%20do%20you%20make%3F%20What%20do%20you%20do%20for%20a%20living%3F%26quot%3B%20You%20don't%20get%20personal%20questions%20like%20that%2C%20which%20I%20find%20to%20be%20refreshing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-moved-to-italy-new-definition-of-success-better-life-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eslower%20pace%20of%20life%3C%2Fa%3E.%20You%20eat%20dinner%20so%20much%20later%2C%20and%20it's%20not%20just%20about%20chowing%20down%20on%20the%20food.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20terrace%20overlooking%20the%20landscape%20in%20Italy.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6aa7b445048b5f68bbae6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221406%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAllan's%20terrace%20in%20Montepulciano%2C%20Italy.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Brad%20Allan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20prices%20are%20different.%20If%20you%20go%20out%20to%20dinner%20here%2C%20you'll%20be%20amazed.%20You%20go%20out%20to%20town%20here%20with%20a%20good%20bottle%20of%20wine%20%E2%80%94%20and%20this%20is%20a%20tourist%20town%20%E2%80%94%20and%20your%20total%20bill%20is%20probably%20going%20to%20be%20%2460%20out%20the%20door.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe're%20also%20able%20to%20take%20trips%20to%20really%20interesting%20places%20with%20Italy%20as%20our%20home%20base.%20Two%20weeks%20ago%2C%20we%20decided%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feverything-you-need-to-know-about-traveling-to-canary-islands-spain%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ego%20to%20Tenerife%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20week%20because%20it%20was%20%2429%20each%20way%20to%20fly%20%E2%80%94%20of%20course%2C%20by%20the%20time%20they%20hit%20you%20with%20bags%2C%20it's%20not%20%2429%20each%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20you%20can%20just%20hop%20on%20a%20plane%20and%20go%20to%20so%20many%20really%20unique%20places%2C%20and%20you%20don't%20have%20issues%20with%20five-hour%20waits%20from%20TSA.%20There's%20an%20ease%20of%20getting%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20never%20take%20trains%20in%20the%20US.%20But%20when%20my%20brother-in-law's%20visiting%2C%20we're%20going%20to%20pop%20down%20to%20Naples%3B%20it's%20only%20two%20and%20a%20half%20hours%20by%20train%20%E2%80%94%20that's%20like%20180%20miles%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20posing%20during%20a%20sunset%20in%20Italy.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6aa7b445048b5f68bbae7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221875%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAllan's%20wife%2C%20Olivia%2C%20in%20Italy.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Brad%20Allan%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%20we%20went%20to%20Scotland%20and%20London%20on%20two%20different%20trips.%20We%20went%20twice%20to%20the%20French%20Alps%20in%20the%20summertime%2C%20because%20it%20gets%20pretty%20warm%20here.%20We%20have%20two%20big%20dogs%2C%20and%20we%20took%20them%20French%20Alps%20so%20they%20could%20swim%20in%20the%20river.%20It's%20beautiful.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20drove%20to%20go%20do%20that%2C%20and%20it%20was%20a%20six-hour%20drive.%20And%20that's%20all%20within%20the%20last%2012%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20really%20nice%20that%20we're%20now%20able%20to%20do%20those%20kinds%20of%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-texas-to-italy-retire-saving-healthcare-costs-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774698361000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6aa7b8e44c01630d317a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-texas-to-italy-retire-saving-healthcare-costs-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Brad%20Allan%20and%20his%20wife%20moved%20from%20Austin%2C%20Texas%2C%20to%20Italy%20to%20retire.%20They're%20saving%20over%20%2420%2C000%20on%20healthcare%20costs%2C%20and%20enjoy%20being%20able%20to%20travel%20more.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jpandy%40insider.com%20(Jordan%20Pandy)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-from-texas-to-italy-retire-saving-healthcare-costs-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%