ir%20own%2C%20traveling%20separately%20during%20their%20respective%20weeks%20at%20camp.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2221b4b40e-09e5-46b9-9340-a0290336d754%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmtrak%20puts%20some%20guardrails%20in%20place%20for%20unaccompanied%20minors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20our%20kids%20were%20under%2016%20when%20we%20started%20doing%20this%20(and%20one%20still%20is)%2C%20we%20needed%20to%20follow%20certain%20rules%2C%20including%20planning%20the%20trip%20between%20two%20crewed%20stations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20booking%20process%20takes%20a%20little%20longer%20than%20when%20buying%20other%20Amtrak%20tickets%20because%20you%20cannot%20make%20a%20reservation%20for%20an%20unaccompanied%20minor%20online%20or%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famtrak-usa-rail-pass-what-to-know-surprises-frequent-traveler-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmtrak%20app%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Instead%2C%20you%20have%20to%20book%20by%20phone%20or%20purchase%20a%20ticket%20at%20a%20station%20with%20a%20ticket%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20make%20the%20reservation%2C%20you're%20given%20instructions%20for%20the%20next%20steps%3A%20Arrive%20at%20least%20one%20hour%20prior%20to%20departure%2C%20and%20be%20ready%20to%20see%20the%20station%20manager%20to%20complete%20some%20paperwork%20to%20confirm%20details%20about%20you%2C%20the%20child%20traveling%2C%20and%20their%20destination.%20It%20doesn't%20take%20long%20to%20complete%20it%20once%20you%20find%20the%20station%20manager%2C%20which%20we%20imagine%20may%20be%20more%20challenging%20at%20larger%20stations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rest%20of%20the%20process%20is%20similarly%20structured%3A%20The%20manager%20gives%20a%20wristband%20to%20the%20child%20traveling%20and%20asks%20them%20a%20few%20basic%20questions%2C%20such%20as%20where%20they%20are%20getting%20off%20the%20train%20and%20who%20is%20meeting%20them%20at%20the%20station.%20You're%20then%20told%20where%20to%20stand%20on%20the%20platform%20and%20which%20car%20your%20child%20should%20board%20when%20the%20train%20arrives.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20kids%20were%20each%20escorted%20onto%20the%20train%20by%20an%20Amtrak%20employee%20and%20shown%20where%20to%20sit.%20Our%20kids%20tend%20to%20be%20seated%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famtrak-food-review-cafe-car-menu-prices-photos-2022-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecaf%C3%A9%20car%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20staffed.%20That%20made%20us%20more%20comfortable%2C%20and%20our%20kids%20consider%20that%20spot%20a%20perk%2C%20since%20passengers%20aren't%20usually%20encouraged%20to%20linger.%20They%20each%20got%20to%20stay%20for%20the%20length%20of%20their%20trip%20and%20even%20had%20a%20table%20to%20themselves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20train%20approaches%20their%20stop%2C%20a%20conductor%20makes%20sure%20the%20traveling%20child%20is%20ready.%20Once%20the%20train%20arrives%20at%20the%20station%20and%20our%20traveler%20is%20in%20the%20care%20of%20their%20grandparents%20or%20us%2C%20off%20they%20go.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22b8950483-eae8-4ff9-b132-3ca1200c8f82%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI'm%20glad%20they%20can%20experience%20this%20small%20act%20of%20independence%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20it%20was%20slightly%20unnerving%20the%20first%20time%20each%20kid%20waved%20goodbye%20from%20the%20train%2C%20it%20feels%20ordinary%20now.%20Our%20son%20enjoys%20looking%20out%20the%20window%20and%20taking%20pictures%20of%20familiar%20places%20along%20the%20route%2C%20and%20our%20daughter%20tends%20to%20spend%20her%20train%20time%20reading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20short%20trip%2C%20but%20we%20appreciate%20that%20they%20can%20exercise%20some%20independence%20and%20enjoy%20the%20train%20on%20their%20own%20during%20the%20day%20and%20for%20short%20distances.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20side%20perk%20is%20that%20they%20have%20been%20earning%20Amtrak%20Guest%20Rewards%20points%20along%20the%20way%2C%20which%20we%20can%20use%20for%20a%20family%20trip%20to%20New%20York%20or%20an%20adventure%20on%20the%20Auto%20Train.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flet-my-kids-take-amtrak-alone-since-preteen-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774696621000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c56893299090a8c09b69b1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flet-my-kids-take-amtrak-alone-since-preteen-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22My%20in-laws%20live%20a%20few%20hours%20away%2C%20and%20each%20summer%2C%20my%20kids%20visit%20their%20grandparents.%20They%20each%20take%20the%20Amtrak%20there%20alone%20and%20love%20it.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Sara%20Clarke)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flet-my-kids-take-amtrak-alone-since-preteen-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Drone%20strike%20rocks%20port%20of%20Salalah%20in%20Oman%3A%20Iran%20military%20confirms%20American%20logistics%20vessel%20targeted%20as%20war%20with%20US-Israel%20escalates%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774696487000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-129863665%2Cimgsize-25468.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fdrone-strike-rocks-port-of-salalah-in-oman-iran-military-confirms-american-logistics-vessel-targeted-as-war-tensions-with-us-israel-escalate%2Farticleshow%2F129863119.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F129863119.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ETensions%20surge%20as%20Iran%20confirms%20targeting%20a%20US-linked%20vessel%20near%20Oman's%20Salalah%20port%2C%20a%20vital%20shipping%20hub.