0in%20person%2C%20and%20workers%20mess%20around%20on%20video%20calls.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWorking-from-home%20(WFH)%20gurus%20said%20hybrid%20work%20is%20a%20nice%20compromise%20that%20addresses%20Dimon's%20concerns.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjamie-dimon-career%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJamie%20Dimon%3C%2Fa%3E%20continued%20his%20crusade%20against%20remote%20work%20this%20week%2C%20launching%20another%20verbal%20barrage%20against%20the%20Zoom%20legions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorking-from-home%20gurus%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20JPMorgan's%20CEO%20made%20some%20good%20points%20%E2%80%94%20but%20didn't%20justify%20a%20full%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcompanies-requiring-return-to-office-rto-mandate%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ereturn%20to%20the%20office%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDimon%20told%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjamie-dimon-peace-middle-east-iran-jpmorgan-ceo-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHill%20and%20Valley%20Forum%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Washington%2C%20D.C.%20on%20Tuesday%20that%20WFH%20simply%20%26quot%3Bdoesn't%20work%26quot%3B%20for%20many%20younger%20employees%2C%20as%20they%20require%20in-person%20training%20from%20more%20senior%20colleagues.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20learn%20by%20going%20on%20a%20sales%20call%20with%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThey%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-wants-to-go-in-office-bosses-dont-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elearn%20by%20seeing%20you%20make%20a%20mistake%3C%2Fa%3E.%20They%20learn%20by%20how%20you%20deal%20with%20the%20mistake.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbillionaire-jamie-dimon-jp-morgan-chase-richest-men-in-banking-2020-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebillionaire%20banker%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20said%20that%20interacting%20and%20collaborating%20in%20person%20helps%20to%20develop%20emotional%20intelligence%2C%20and%20effective%20management%20is%20virtually%20impossible%20over%20video%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere's%20very%20little%20follow-up%2C%20a%20lot%20more%20game%20playing%2C%20you%20know%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foil-prices-crude-lng-iran-brent-steve-hanke-ali-hormuz-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erope-a-dope%3C%2Fa%3E%20type%20of%20politics%2C%26quot%3B%20Dimon%20said.%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20people%20aren't%20paying%20attention%20at%20all.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMiming%20someone%20looking%20down%20at%20their%20phone%2C%20he%20said%20that%20%26quot%3Bpeople%20on%20the%20Zoom%2C%20they're%20texting%20each%20other.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20go%20to%20a%20meeting%20with%20me%2C%20you've%20got%20my%20full%20friggin'%20attention%20the%20whole%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20boss%20of%20America's%20largest%20bank%20by%20assets%20issued%20a%20pointed%20reminder%20that%20a%20company's%20first%20priority%20should%20be%20to%20make%20its%20customers%20happy%2C%20not%20its%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHow%20would%20you%20feel%20if%20it%20was%20all%20about%20making%20the%20employee%20happy%2C%20as%20opposed%20to%20getting%20your%20well-cooked%20steak%20or%20your%20martini%20on%20time%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c383fb6e-17d6-4e1a-bd41-2c107b30211a%5C%22%3EBest%20of%20both%20worlds%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwork-from-home-wfh-downsides-dads-parenting-childcare-remote-office-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENicholas%20Bloom%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20Stanford%20economics%20professor%20and%20cofounder%20of%20WFH%20Research%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20by%20email%20that%20Dimon%20made%20%26quot%3Bsome%20good%20points.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20%26quot%3Byounger%20employees%20in%20an%20apprenticeship%20business%20like%20finance%2C%20you%20probably%20want%20them%20in%20three%20or%20four%20days%20a%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20Bloom%20argued%20that%20outside%20a%20few%20specialist%20roles%20like%20traders%2C%20five%20days%20in%20the%20office%20isn't%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20workers%2C%20especially%20those%20who%20are%20five-plus%20years%20into%20their%20career%2C%20%26quot%3Bneed%20a%20day%20a%20week%20to%20read%2C%20think%2C%20write%20performance%20reviews%2C%20presentations%2C%20client%20pitches%2C%20etc%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20stuff%20is%20best%20done%20in%20a%20quiet%20environment%2C%20and%20that%20is%20typically%20at%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBloom%20said%20WFH%20skeptics%20often%20pick%20on%20fully%20remote%20work%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bstraw%20man%20to%20destroy%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20fail%20to%20explain%20why%20hybrid%20work%20isn't%20a%20viable%20compromise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BElon%20Musk%20is%20a%20master%20of%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20hybrid%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bpretty%20amazing%20system%20and%20hard%20to%20beat.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20like%20saying%20you%20don't%20drink%20because%20if%20you%20drink%2010%20beers%20you%20pass%20out%20%E2%80%94%20well%2C%20you%20can%20drink%20one%20beer%20and%20enjoy%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Bloom%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERavi%20Gajendran%2C%20a%20leadership%20and%20management%20professor%20at%20Florida%20International%20University%2C%20agreed%20that%20some%20of%20Dimon's%20concerns%20are%20%26quot%3Bperhaps%20less%20relevant%20in%20a%20hybrid%20world.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGajendran%20said%20the%20bank%20chief's%20comments%20were%20too%20focused%20on%20the%20downsides%20of%20remote%20work.%20He%20cited%20research%20showing%20the%20%26quot%3Bbenefits%20of%20flexibility%20outweigh%20the%20costs%20of%20isolation%20for%20key%20outcomes%20such%20as%20job%20satisfaction%2C%20commitment%2C%20performance%2C%20and%20turnover%20intentions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20remote%20work%20makes%20employees%20more%20satisfied%2C%20committed%2C%20and%20productive%2C%20that%20should%20ultimately%20benefit%20customers%2C%26quot%3B%20Gajendran%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22207ec76b-6531-4db7-a9c9-44c6d38992d7%5C%22%3ELong-running%20battle%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EDimon%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjamie-dimon-every-comment-work-from-home-employee-remote-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erailing%20against%20remote%20work%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20years%20now.%20He's%20warned%20that%20it%20hinders%20innovation%20and%20information%20sharing%2C%20slows%20decision-making%2C%20reduces%20efficiency%2C%20and%20fosters%20politics%20and%20bureaucracy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRemote%20work%20eliminates%20much%20spontaneous%20learning%20and%20creativity%20because%20you%20don't%20run%20into%20people%20at%20the%20coffee%20machine%2C%20talk%20with%20clients%20in%20unplanned%20scenarios%2C%20or%20travel%20to%20meet%20with%20customers%20and%20employees%20for%20feedback%20on%20your%20products%20and%20services%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20in%20his%20shareholder%20letter%20for%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDimon%20%E2%80%94%20who%20ordered%20a%20firm-wide%2C%20full-time%20return%20to%20the%20office%20roughly%20a%20year%20ago%20%E2%80%94%20issued%20a%20colorful%20tirade%20against%20WFH%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjamie-dimons-viral-remote-work-criticisms-draw-supporters-haters-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eleaked%20audio%20recording%3C%2Fa%3E%20obtained%20by%20Business%20Insider%20early%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20call%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20on%20Fridays%2C%20and%20there's%20not%20a%20goddamn%20person%20you%20can%20get%20a%20hold%20of%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDimon%20is%20far%20from%20the%20only%20business%20leader%20to%20oppose%20remote%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFormer%20Google%20CEO%20Eric%20Schmidt%20said%20last%20year%20that%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feric-schmidt-google-wfh-work-life-balance-learning-tech-ai-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Elearned%20a%20great%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20listening%20to%20older%20coworkers%20argue%20in%20the%20early%20years%20of%20his%20career.%20%26quot%3BHow%20do%20you%20recreate%20that%20in%20this%20new%20thing%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20queried.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Tesla%20and%20SpaceX%2C%20has%20said%20it's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-remote-work-morally-wrong-get-off-high-horse-2023-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eunfair%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Blaptop%20classes%26quot%3B%20expect%20to%20stay%20at%20home%20while%20others%20go%20into%20work%20to%20make%20their%20cars%2C%20deliver%20their%20food%2C%20and%20fix%20their%20homes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20world's%20richest%20man%20said%20the%20WFH%20crowd%20is%20so%20%26quot%3Bdetached%20from%20reality%26quot%3B%20that%20it%20gives%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-work-from-home-crowd-detached-from-reality-tesla-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMarie%20Antoinette%20vibes%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-jamie-dimon-remote-work-wfh-office-return-musk-schmidt-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774695781000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6a8ed445048b5f68bbad0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjpmorgan-jamie-dimon-remote-work-wfh-office-return-musk-schmidt-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22JPMorgan%20CEO%20Jamie%20Dimon%20said%20remote%20work%20hinders%20training%2C%20hurts%20collaboration%2C%20and%20feeds%20distrac