20seize%20the%20safe's%20contents%2C%20they%20left%20them%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20floor%20with%20the%20hard%20drives%20and%20binders%20piled%20on%20top%2C%20agent%20Kelly%20Maguire%20testified%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fghislaine-maxwell-sentenced-20-years-prison-sex-trafficking-jeffrey-epstein-2022-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20criminal%20trial%20of%20Epstein's%20co-conspirator%20Ghislaine%20Maxwell%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFive%20days%20later%2C%20when%20the%20FBI%20returned%20to%20the%20mansion%20with%20a%20new%20warrant%20in%20hand%2C%20the%20safe's%20contents%20were%20gone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%20that%20day%2C%20the%20items%20were%20handed%20over%20to%20the%20FBI%20in%20the%20form%20of%20two%20suitcases%20by%20Richard%20Kahn%2C%20Epstein's%20longtime%20accountant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20episode%20has%20fueled%20speculation%20among%20watchers%20of%20the%20Epstein%20story%20amid%20broader%20concerns%20about%20cover-ups%20and%20undue%20influence%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhy%20Kahn%20took%20the%20safe's%20contents%2C%20and%20what%20he%20did%20with%20them%2C%20has%20been%20a%20mystery%20%E2%80%94%20until%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20March%2011%20testimony%20before%20the%20House%20Oversight%20Committee%2C%20Kahn%20said%20that%20the%20safe's%20contents%20passed%20through%20three%20different%20people%20before%20coming%20into%20the%20FBI's%20possession.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22396%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22jeffrey%20epstein%20safe%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6e6ca8e5f53c45ea2d007%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22306%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThis%20photo%20of%20Jeffrey%20Epstein's%20sawed-open%20safe%2C%20with%20hard%20drives%20and%20other%20items%20piled%20on%20top%2C%20was%20shown%20to%20jurors%20at%20Ghislaine%20Maxwell's%20trial.%3Cp%3EUS%20Department%20of%20Justice%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeffrey-epstein-accountant-lawyer-explain-finances-congress-house-oversight-testimony-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20deposition%20made%20public%20Tuesday%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Kahn%20said%20he%20was%20informed%20of%20the%20raid%20by%20Merwin%20Dela%20Cruz%2C%20the%20manager%20of%20Epstein's%20Upper%20East%20Side%20mansion%2C%20who%20said%20he%20packed%20the%20safe's%20contents%20into%20two%20suitcases%20and%20left%20them%20with%20Kahn's%20doorman%20in%20Manhattan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20FBI%20broke%20into%20Epstein's%20home%2C%20they%20broke%20down%20his%20door%2C%20so%20his%20door%20could%20not%20lock%20and%20the%20alarm%20could%20not%20set%20properly%2C%26quot%3B%20Kahn%20told%20the%20committee.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20Merwin%2C%20the%20house%20manager%2C%20was%20at%20the%20house%2C%20he%20realized%20that%20these%20items%20were%20not%20safe%20to%20be%20left%20alone.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKahn%2C%20who%20wasn't%20in%20New%20York%20City%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20raid%2C%20said%20he%20took%20possession%20of%20the%20items%20%26quot%3Bthree%20or%20four%20days%20later.%26quot%3B%20He%20testified%20that%20he%20brought%20the%20two%20bags%20into%20his%20apartment%20and%20didn't%20look%20inside%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20never%20touched%20them.%20I%20never%20opened%20them%2C%26quot%3B%20Kahn%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20left%20them%20in%20my%20dining%20room.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20day%20or%20two%20later%2C%20Dela%20Cruz%20called%20Kahn%20again%20to%20say%20the%20FBI%20was%20looking%20for%20the%20stuff%20they%20had%20left%20behind%2C%20Kahn%20told%20the%20committee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20when%20he%20grabbed%20the%20bags%20from%20his%20home%20and%20brought%20them%20to%20the%20FBI%20agents%20at%20Epstein's%20house%2C%20Kahn%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReached%20by%20Business%20Insider%2C%20Dela%20Cruz%20declined%20to%20comment.%20Daniel%20Ruzumna%2C%20an%20attorney%20representing%20Kahn%2C%20declined%20to%20comment%20beyond%20Kahn's%20testimony.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20Maxwell's%20trial%2C%20Maguire%20testified%20that%20the%20contents%20of%20the%20suitcases%20%26quot%3Bappeared%20to%20be%20all%20of%20the%20items%20that%20had%20been%20previously%20located%20in%20the%20safe.%26quot%3B%20In%20a%20court%20filing%2C%20prosecutors%20said%20the%20safe's%20stash%20included%2048%20loose%20diamonds%2C%20which%20is%20the%20same%20number%20of%20diamonds%20Epstein%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeffrey-epstein-planned-inheritance-marriage-karyna-shuliak-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebequeathed%20to%20his%20fianc%C3%A9e%2C%20Karyna%20Shuliak%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20awaiting%20trial%20on%20sex-trafficking%20charges%20before%20his%20jailhouse%20suicide.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d4c8442d-e03f-4c27-b855-230a74d189ad%5C%22%3EThe%20missing%20Palm%20Beach%20hard%20drives%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20testimony%20released%20by%20the%20committee%20on%20Tuesday%20also%20shed%20light%20on%20the%20fate%20of%20computers%20removed%20from%20Epstein's%20Palm%20Beach%2C%20Florida%2C%20house%20shortly%20before%20police%20officers%20executed%20a%20search%20warrant%20there%20in%202005%2C%20during%20a%20local%20investigation%20into%20his%20interactions%20with%20underage%20girls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFlorida%20law%20enforcement%20officials%20never%20found%20the%20computers.%20Their%20investigation%20culminated%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fghislaine-maxwell-appeals-conviction-jeffrey-epstein-non-prosecution-agreement-juror-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20plea%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20required%20Epstein%20to%20serve%20a%20year%20in%20jail%20%E2%80%94%20after%20which%20he%20resumed%20his%20business%20and%20social%20lives%2C%20interacting%20with%20many%20rich%2C%20famous%2C%20and%20powerful%20figures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22652%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jeffrey%20Epstein%20palm%20beach%20house%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6e7ac8373a547629c7382%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22433%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJeffrey%20Epstein's%20Palm%20Beach%20house%2C%20which%20the%20police%20searched%20for%20evidence%20in%202005.%3Cp%3EUS%20Department%20of%20Justice%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20March%2019%20deposition%20with%20the%20House%20Oversight%20Committee%2C%20Darren%20Indyke%2C%20Epstein's%20longtime%20personal%20attorney%2C%20said%20he%20learned%20after%20Epstein's%202008%20conviction%20that%20the%20hard%20drives%20were%20in%20the%20possession%20of%20Riley%20Kiraly%2C%20a%20private%20investigations%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fepstein%2Ffiles%2FDataSet%252010%2FEFTA01733753.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ean%20October%202005%20memo%3C%2Fa%3E%20released%20by%20the%20Justice%20Department%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Epstein%20files%2C%20firm%20co-owner%20William%20Riley%20told%20one%20of%20Epstein's%20lawyers%20that%20an%20employee%20had%20retrieved%20computers%20from%20Epstein's%20home%2C%20among%20other%20items%20of%20%26quot%3Bpotential%20evidentiary%20value.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20Epstein's%20Florida%20criminal%20case%20concluded%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.justice.gov%2Fepstein%2Ffiles%2FDataSet%25209%2FEFTA00884246.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERiley%20asked%20Epstein%20and%20his%20lawyers%3C%2Fa%3E%20what%20he%20should%20do%20with%20items%20belonging%20to%20Epstein%2C%20the%20DOJ's%20files%20show.%20He%20said%20they%20included%20computer%20hard%20drives%2C%20which%20were%20cloned%20%26quot%3Bby%20a%20forensic%20specialist%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Blocked%20in%20storage.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERiley%20declined%20to%20comment%20to%20Business%20Insider.%20Indyke%20said%20in%20the%20deposition%20that%20he%20didn't%20know%20anything%20about%20the%20storage%20units.%20The%20Epstein%20files%20show%20that%20Kahn%20was%20in%20charge%20of%20paying%20the%20fees%20for%20the%20storage%20site%2C%20but%20he%20wasn't%20asked%20about%20them%20in%20his%20deposition.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20Democrats%20on%20the%20House%20Oversight%20Committee%20sent%20letters%20to%20Riley%20and%20two%20other%20private%20investigators%20who%20worked%20for%20Epstein%2C%20asking%20about%20the%20computers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Committee%20requests%20that%20you%20make%20yourself%20available%20for%20a%20transcribed%20interview%20to%20provide%20insight%20into%20the%20contents%2C%20removal%2C%20storage%2C%20and%20location%20of%20materials%20removed%20from%20Mr.%20Epstein's%20Palm%20Beach%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20letter%20to%20Riley%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeffrey-epstein-safe-diamonds-hard-drives-evidence-what-happened-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1774692061000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6ed718e5f53c45ea2d07e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeffrey-epstein-safe-diamonds-hard-drives-evidence-what-happened-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22New%20testimony%20shows%20Jeffrey%20Epstein's%20diamonds%2C%20passports%2C%20and%20hard%20drives%20passed%20through%20three%20people%20before%20returning%20to%20the%20FBI%20after%20a%202019%20raid.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jshamsian%40businessinsider.com%20(Jacob%20Shamsian)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeffrey-epstein-safe-diamonds-hard-drives-evidence-what-happened-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20best%20throw%20blankets%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EWhen%20you%20buy%20through%20our%20links%2C%20Business%20Insider