%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGarnet%20Hill%20Gingham%20Check%20Cotton%20Throw%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20re-released%20from%20a%201992%20archival%20design%20to%20celebrate%2050%20years%20of%20the%20brand%20in%20partnership%20with%20Bedford%20Collections.%20Master%20weavers%20made%20these%20blankets%20on%20antique%20looms.%20When%20you%20look%20closer%20at%20the%20classic%20gingham%20print%2C%20available%20in%20blue%20or%20green%2C%20you'll%20notice%20the%20level%20of%20detail%20that%20went%20into%20the%20print%2C%20with%20a%20beautiful%20checkerboard%20print%20within%20the%20gingham.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20gingham%20cotton%20blanket%20folded%20up%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6f6428373a547629c7422%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20cotton%20Garnet%20Hill%20gingham%20blanket%20easily%20folds%20to%20take%20up%20minimal%20space.%3Cp%3EJaclyn%20Turner%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHeirloom%20quality%20with%20a%20bespoke%20feel.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20cotton%20fabric%20is%20thick%20and%20durable%20(reinforced%20with%20a%20turn%20back%20hem)%20with%20a%20slight%20heft.%20It's%20textured%2C%20while%20soft%20to%20the%20touch.%20My%20only%20drawback%20to%20the%20throw%20is%20that%20it's%20dimensions%20are%20a%20bit%20narrow%2C%20measuring%2043%20by%2062%20inches%2C%20instead%20of%20the%20typical%2050%20by%2060%20inches.%20I%20wish%20it%20was%20just%20a%20bit%20wider.%20The%20blanket%20is%20also%20available%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3Ddd8548a91919d7110cb8c61673415c22c4ddcc9ee8b0de542ba7ec9ee34ccc62%26postID%3D69c6d71c5ebd47b37d013482%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fbest-throw-blankets%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.garnethill.com%252Fgingham-check-cotton-blanket%252F727620%5C%22%20d