t%3B%20by%2070%20inches%20and%2060%20by%2080%20inches)%20and%2010%20colors%2C%20finished%20with%20a%20fringe%20edges.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22quince%20throw%20blanket%20next%20to%20accent%20pillows%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6f6fff573a637a756715a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EQuince's%20Mongolian%20Cashmere%20Throw%20is%20a%20luxurious%20addition%20to%20a%20sofa.%20%3Cp%3EJaclyn%20Turner%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHistorically%2C%20wool%20can%20be%20scratchy%2C%20but%20not%20this%20cashmere%20throw.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20It's%20smooth%20and%20felt-like.%20It%20looks%20luxurious%20and%20elegant%20when%20draped%20over%20a%20sofa.%20It%20feels%20more%20formal%20in%20design%2C%20something%20I%20use%20in%20my%20living%20room%20as%20opposed%20to%20layering%20on%20my%20bed.%20I%20haven't%20noticed%20much%20pilling%2C%20but%20it%20does%20get%20linty%20on%20my%20clothes.%20While%20most%20cashmere%20is%20dry%20clean%20only%2C%20this%20one%20should%20be%20hand%20washed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e39ae413-e41c-4b7d-9a11-27ef214596f7%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Best%20weighted%5C%22%3EBest%20weighted%20blanket%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EForm%20and%20function.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI%20love%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3D7d7f071f9ec8cfb6a3de354c8b6fbb5e15e3515a1d6844836971925c883a06f3%26postID%3D69c6d71c5ebd47b37d013482%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fbest-throw-blankets%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fbearaby.com%252Fproducts%252Fthe-napper%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBearaby%20Cotton%20Weighted%20Blanket%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%20it%20doesn't%20look%20like%20an%20ordinary%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-weighted-blanket%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eweighted%20blanket%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20this%20is%20one%20I'm%20proud%20to%20leave%20out%20on%20display.%20That's%20a%20major%20pro%2C%20because%20the%20weight%20can%20make%20the%20a%20little%20more%20difficult%20to%20take%20from%20room%20to%20room.%20The%20chunky%20knit%20design%20is%20made%20purely%20of%20organic%20cotton%3B%20layers%20and%20layers%20of%20cotton%20are%20layered%20to%20create%20natural%2C%20even%20weight%20as%20opposed%20to%20glass%20beads%20or%20pellets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20navy%20blanket%20sits%20on%20a%20gray%20couch%20with%20a%20Kansas%20State%20pillow.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F680bebb8c6ad288d147f38ff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Bearaby%20Cotton%20Napper%20gets%20its%20weight%20from%20its%20heavyweight%20knit%20fabric.%3Cp%3EKinsley%20Searles%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECalming%20comfort.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Weighted%20blankets%20are%20known%20to%20improve%20sleep%20quality%2C%20lowers%20stress%2C%20and%20eases%20anxiety.%20You%20should%20select%20a%20weighted%20blanket%20that%20is%2010%25%20of%20your%20body%20weight.%20Bearaby's%20is%20available%20in%20weight%20increments%20ranging%20from%2010%20to%2025%20pounds%20in%20seven%20colors.%20The%20dimensions%20vary%20based%20on%20the%20size%20you%20get%2C%20ranging%20from%2040%20by%2064%20inches%20to%2048%20by%2072%20inches.%20Bearaby%20also%20offers%20a%20queen%20and%20king%20blanket%20that%20weigh%2020%20and%2025%20pounds%2C%20respectively%2C%20and%20kids%20sizes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOne%20catch%2C%20literally.%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20handwoven%20design%20actually%20helps%20with%20breathability%2C%20making%20it%20a%20great%20option%20if%20you're%20concerned%20about%20overheating.%20However%2C%20fingers%20and%20toes%20can%20get%20caught%20in%20fabric%20and%20cause%20it%20to%20stretch%2C%20which%20is%20something%20to%20keep%20in%20mind%20with%20any%20open%20weave%20design%2C%20though%20the%20weight%20truly%20highlights%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%226d241466-ff54-4d43-8066-9f6440053a3d%5C%22%3EMore%20weighted%20blankets%20we%20recommend%3A%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223bab1f6b-d3d2-4534-9479-f9b3b0b35da7%5C%22%3EA%20note%20on%20wool%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20wool%20blanket%20category%20has%20been%20tricky%3B%20alot%20of%20the%20ones%20I've%20tested%20previously%20and%20enjoyed%20are%20no%20longer%20available.%20The%20insights%20from%20my%20team%20have%20also%20been%20limited%20thanks%20to%20several%20staffers%20with%20wool%20allergies%20or%20just%20an%20aversion%20to%20wool%20in%20favor%20of%20softer%20or%20lighter%20fabrics.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22583eab0f-885d-4ef0-82dd-53c574213169%5C%22%3EHere%20are%20some%20options%20from%20trusted%20brands%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22837f8b03-647f-496f-9797-28be470a846a%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20to%20consider%5C%22%3EWhat%20to%20consider%20when%20buying%20a%20throw%20blanket%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFinding%20the%20best%20throw%20blanket%20will%20likely%20start%20with%20price%20and%20material%2C%20but%20there%20are%20a%20few%20other%20things%20to%20consider%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESize%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EMost%20throw%20blankets%20typically%20measure%20around%2050%20by%2060%20inches%2C%20so%20they%20may%20not%20be%20long%20enough%20for%20taller%20people%20or%20those%20who%20want%20to%20share.%20If%20you're%20planning%20on%20using%20the%20blanket%20to%20curl%20up%20with%20someone%20else%2C%20you'll%20want%20to%20look%20for%20an%20oversize%20option.%20Pay%20attention%20to%20dimensions.%20If%20you%20want%20something%20that%20covers%20the%20full-size%20of%20your%20bed%2C%20look%20for%20bed%20blankets%20in%20standard%20bed%20sizing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMaterial%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20What%20you%20choose%20will%20depend%20on%20how%20you%20plan%20to%20use%20the%20blanket%20and%20your%20budget.%20Wool%20is%20warm%20but%20can%20be%20itchy.%20Fleece%20is%20soft%20but%20not%20as%20durable.%20Cotton%20is%20breathable%20while%20down%20is%20insulating.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECare%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20If%20you%20have%20pets%20or%20kids%20or%20plan%20on%20washing%20the%20blanket%20often%2C%20you'll%20want%20something%20that%20can%20be%20machine-washed.%20Polyester%20and%20cotton%20(including%20fleece%20and%20faux%20fur)%20can%20typically%20go%20in%20the%20washing%20machine%2C%20while%20wool%20and%20cashmere%20are%20often%20dry-clean%20only.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDesign%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESince%20many%20people%20leave%20their%20blankets%20on%20display%2C%20throws%20come%20in%20a%20huge%20variety%20of%20styles%20and%20colors.%20Consider%20a%20color%20that%20coordinates%20well%20with%20your%20decor%20and%20perhaps%20adds%20some%20interesting%20texture%20to%20a%20couch%20or%20chair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221b1a2f8f-a01e-48bd-a43c-6da45143fe1b%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20we%20tested%5C%22%3EHow%20we%20tested%20the%20best%20throw%20blankets%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20dog%20sits%20across%20fourblankets%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c6f77d8e5f53c45ea2d0cb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20had%20a%20little%20help%20on%20insights%20with%20an%20expert%20furry%20tester.%3Cp%3EJaclyn%20Turner%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20this%20guide%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20my%20hands-on%20experience%20with%20over%20a%20dozen%20throw%20blankets%2C%20I%20consulted%20with%20fellow%20editors%20about%20the%20blankets%20they%20keep%20on%20rotation%2C%20and%20what%20they%20like%20about%20them.%20For%20each%20blanket%2C%20I%20not%20only%20consider%20the%20aesthetic%20and%20color%20options%2C%20but%20sizing%2C%20comfort%20and%20warmth%2C%20long%20term%20durability%2C%20and%20ease%20of%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229a620f7f-6c49-4b1d-af94-5ec64b201581%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Meet%20the%20expert%5C%22%3EMeet%20the%20expert%20behind%20the%20guide%3A%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJaclyn%20Turner%2C%20senior%20home%20editor%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EI've%20had%20the%20pleasure%20of%20having%20hands%20on%20experience%20with%20almost%20every%20major%20bedding%20brand%2C%20after%20reviewing%20countless%20of%20the%20best%20bedding%20products.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20throw%20blankets%2C%20I%20definitely%20gravitate%20toward%20the%20softest%2C%20fluffiest%20blankets%20and%20have%20a%20bin%20overflowing%20with%20a%20bevy%20of%20options.%20My%20oldest%20throw%20blankets%20still%20in%20use%20is%20tied%20with%20a%20fleece%20Room%20Essentials%20throw%20from%20Target%20that%20I%20got%20when%20I%20went%20off%20to%20college%20and%20a%20twin-size%20fleece%20blanket%20I%20picked%20up%20at%20Zara%20Home%20while%20studying%20abroad.%20However%2C%20my%20current%20obsession%20is%20undoubtedly%20The%20Lola%20Blanket.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2236e5ce62-0a6f-44ea-89d6-569e12542f28%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Throw%20blanket%20FAQs%5C%22%3EThrow%20blanket%20FAQs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20a%20throw%20blanket%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EA%20throw%20blanket%20are%20smaller%20than%20comforters%2C%20and%20typically%20meant%20to%20be%20used%20by%20one%20person.%20The%20standard%20size%20for%20a%20throw%20blanket%20is%20typically%2050%20by%2060%20inches.%20They're%20great%20to%20layer%20across%20sofas%2C%20chairs%2C%20or%20beds%20for%20both%20decor%20and%20easy%20access%20when%20you're%20in%20need%20of%20a%20little%20warmth.%20Due%20to%20the%20smaller%20size%2C%20they're%20also%20more%20convenient%20to%20take%20along%20if%20you're%20traveling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20size%20is%20a%20throw%20blanket%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EA%20typical%20size%20for%20a%20throw%20blanket%20is%2050%20by%2060%20inches%2C%20but%20you%20can%20find%20a%20wide%20variety%20of%20sizes.%20Taller%20people%20or%20those%20wanting%20to%20share%20should%20look%20for%20oversized%20throws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3EHow%20do%20you%20style%20a%20throw%20blanket%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThrow%20blankets%20are%20a%20simple%20way%20to%20add%20a%20bit%20of%20bright%20color%20or%20interesting%20texture%20to%20your%20living%20room.%20Try%20picking%20a%20color%20from%20a%20favorite%20painting%20or%20patterned%20rug%20and%20choosing%20a%20blanket%20that%20either%20coordinates%20or%20contrasts%20with%20that%20color.%20You%20can%20arrange%20it%20by%20folding%20it%20or%20draping%20across%20a%20sofa%20or%20chair%20arm%2C%20or%20alongside%20the%20edge%20of%20a%20bed.%20People%20will%20also%20display%20their%20favorite%20blankets%20on%20blanket%20ladders%20or%20have%20them%20peaking%20out%20of%20baskets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3ECan%20you%20sleep%20with%20a%20throw%20blanket%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20they're%20typically%20smaller%2C%20a%20throw%20blanket%20may%20not%20fully%20cover%20you%2C%20but%20you%20can%20absolutely%20use%20one%20while%20you%20sleep.%20They%20can%20add%20extra%20warmth%20in%20conjunction%20with%20your%20comforter.%20Before%20you%20decide%20to%20sleep%20under%20it%20regularly%2C%20you%20may%20want%20to%20consider%20how%20easy%20it%20is%20to%20wash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat%20is%20Oeko-Tex%20certification%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EMany%20of%20the%20throw%20blankets%20listed%20have%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oeko-tex.com%2Fen%2Four-standards%2Fstandard-100-by-oeko-tex%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStandard%20100%20by%20Oeko%20Tex%20certification%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20means%20the%20fabrics%20have%20been%20independently%20tested%20for%20over%20100%20harmful%20chemical%20substances%20and%20are%20safe%20for%20human%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%