0assembling%20Ikea%20furniture%20last%20year.%20It%20gave%20me%20the%20flexibility%20to%20run%20my%20own%20business%20and%20farm.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22887%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sandra%20Navarro%2C%20who%20assembles%20furniture%20for%20Taskrabbit%2C%20wears%20a%20purple%20t-shirt%20and%20dark%20baseball%20cap%20while%20posing%20against%20a%20beige%20background.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c537a1299090a8c09b67cc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22665%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESandra%20Navarro%20said%20she%20has%20carved%20out%20a%20niche%20on%20Taskrabbit%2C%20assembling%20dressers%20from%20Ikea.%3Cp%3ESandra%20Navarro%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESandra%20Navarro%20works%20on%20Taskrabbit%20and%20runs%20her%20own%20handyman%20business%20in%20Arizona.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20has%20a%20specialty%20that%20gets%20her%20gigs%3A%20assembling%20Ikea%20furniture.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELast%20year%2C%20Navarro%20made%20%2437%2C000%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-labor-market-disruptions-taskrabbit-jobs-opportunities-ceo-ania-smith-2026-2%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETaskrabbit%20as%20a%20gig%20worker.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Sandra%20Navarro%2C%20a%2033-year-old%20who%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftraveled-america-finding-best-us-city-live-in-tucson-arizona-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Elives%20in%20Arizona%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20and%20assembles%20furniture%20for%20customers%20on%20Taskrabbit.%20Business%20Insider%20verified%20her%20earnings.%20The%20interview%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20originally%20saw%20an%20advertisement%20for%20Taskrabbit%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-moved-new-york-city-to-connecticut-drawbacks-benefits-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENew%20York%3C%2Fa%3E%20several%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eit%20wasn't%20available%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-los-angeles-to-phoenix-for-job-big-mistake-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPhoenix%20area%3C%2Fa%3E.%20But%20later%2C%20when%20I%20was%20leaving%20the%20restaurant%20industry%2C%20I%20checked%20again%2C%20and%20the%20company%20was%20starting%20to%20accept%20Phoenix%20applicants.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20worked%20in%20restaurants%20for%20two%20decades.%20I%20started%20at%20the%20bottom%20as%20a%20busser%20and%20worked%20my%20way%20up%20the%20service%20side.%20I%20went%20as%20high%20up%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwalmart-store-manager-job-typical-day-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estore%20manager%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20also%20tended%20bar%20and%2C%20toward%20the%20end%20of%20my%20career%2C%20became%20a%20kitchen%20manager.%20I%20was%20very%20sleep-deprived%20and%20overweight%20from%20the%20work%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20Taskrabbit%2C%20I%20set%20my%20own%20schedule.%20I%20have%20a%20farm%20and%20my%20own%20handyman%20business%2C%20so%20I%20schedule%20tasks%20in%20between%20those%20commitments.%20My%20time%20is%20very%20limited%2C%20and%20having%20the%20ability%20to%20pick%20and%20choose%20and%20create%20my%20schedule%20is%20so%20critical.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20always%20been%20pretty%20handy%20with%20furniture%20assembly.%20The%20majority%20of%20what%20I%20do%20for%20Taskrabbit%20is%20assemble%20Ikea%20furniture%2C%20though%20I%20also%20see%20a%20lot%20of%20items%20from%20Wayfair%20and%20Amazon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20common%20item%20I%20assemble%20is%20dressers.%20Folks%20normally%20want%20to%20tackle%20it%20on%20their%20own%2C%20then%20see%20all%20the%20pieces%20and%20think%2C%20%26quot%3BNope%2C%20this%20is%20not%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20found%20my%20niche%20within%20Ikea's%20Pax%20wardrobe%20system.%20It%20can%20be%20a%20stand-alone%20dresser%20against%20a%20wall%20or%20an%20entire%20walk-in%20closet%2C%20depending%20on%20how%20it%20is%20assembled.%20I've%20played%20around%20with%20an%20in-store%20tool%20Ikea%20offers%20that%20lets%20you%20customize%20it%2C%20so%20I've%20become%20familiar%20with%20this%20particular%20piece%20of%20furniture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20I%20made%20about%20%2437%2C000%20in%20gross%20income%20from%20Taskrabbit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOutside%20Taskrabbit%2C%20I%20mount%20TVs%20on%20walls%2C%20assemble%20furniture%2C%20put%20up%20photos%2C%20and%20do%20other%20work%20through%20my%20handyman%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20personal%20suggestion%20for%20anyone%20doing%20gig%20work%20is%20to%20read%20the%20book%20%26quot%3BProfit%20First%26quot%3B%20by%20Mike%20Michalowicz.%20It%20shows%20you%20how%20to%20set%20yourself%20up%20not%20only%20to%20collect%20profit%20but%20also%20to%20tuck%20away%20money%20for%20taxes%20and%20other%20expenses%20that%20come%20up%20in%20your%20business.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20gig%20worker%2C%20managing%20your%20own%20business%20and%20finances%20is%20crucial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDo%20you%20have%20a%20story%20to%20share%20about%20Taskrabbit%20or%20gig%20work%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabitter%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Eabitter%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20via%20encrypted%20messaging%20app%20Signal%20at%20808-854-4501.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20WiFi%20network%2C%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehere's%20our%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-po