-doesnt-flinch-explained%2Famp_articleshow%2F129861357.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20always%20wanted%20to%20live%20in%20Europe%2C%20so%20I%20bought%20a%20tiny%20home%20in%20the%20Netherlands%20when%20my%20son%20moved%20out.%20Now%2C%20I'm%20leaving.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Side%20by%20side%20of%20Sidra%20Gifford%20and%20her%20tiny%20home%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c2abc758b5806618e7dccd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESidra%20Gifford%20moved%20from%20the%20US%20to%20the%20Netherlands.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Sidra%20Gifford%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ESidra%20Gifford%2C%2052%2C%20is%20from%20the%20US%20but%20wanted%20to%20live%20elsewhere%20since%20she%20was%20a%20teenager.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIn%202025%2C%20she%20moved%20from%20the%20Bay%20Area%20to%20Minitopia%2C%20a%20tiny%20home%20village%20in%20the%20Netherlands.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EWhile%20Gifford%20said%20she%20like%20this%20style%20of%20living%2C%20she's%20selling%20her%20tiny%20house%20after%20six%20months.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Sidra%20Gifford%2C%2052%2C%20a%20therapist%20from%20Woodstock%2C%20New%20York.%20She%20moved%20from%20the%20Bay%20Area%20to%20Valkenswaard%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3Ethe%20Netherlands%2C%20in%202025.%20This%20piece%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20I%20was%20a%20teenager%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20wasn't%20meant%20to%20live%20in%20the%20US.%20It%20never%20aligned%20with%20my%20values.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20my%2020s%2C%20I%20worked%20at%20a%20Dutch%20university%20and%20always%20wanted%20to%20return.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20my%20son%20finished%20high%20school%20and%20I%20became%20an%20empty%20nester%2C%20the%20Netherlands%20was%20at%20the%20top%20of%20my%20list%20of%20places%20to%20move%20to.%20In%20July%202025%2C%20at%20age%2051%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcouple-60s-built-tiny-home-mortgage-free-pros-cons-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EI%20moved%20to%20Minitopia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20tiny%20home%20village%20in%20the%20south%20of%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221958%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sidra%20Gifford's%20tiny%20home%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69c2ac1c5b58f1f0f9336988%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221306%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20exterior%20of%20Gifford's%20home.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Sidra%20Gifford%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESix%20months%20later%2C%20I'm%20preparing%20to%20sell%20that%20home%20and%20leave%20the%20Netherlands%20in%20search%20of%20another%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbuilt-tiny-home-house-using-chatgpt-ai-useful-guidance-was-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Etiny%20house.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider's%20Joshua%20Nelken-Zitser%20spent%20several%20nights%20in%20Minitopia%2C%20a%20tiny%20home%20village%20in%20the%20Netherlands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20story%20is%20part%20of%20his%20series%20exploring%20how%20living%20in%20the%20villages%20has%20affected%20residents'%20careers%2C%20lives%2C%20and%20finances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c7d9a7f4-12bf-442f-bbb4-ebd7db25cb0c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI've%20always%20been%20fascinated%20by%20homemade%20houses%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmistakes-american-family-made-moving-to-the-netherlands-leaving-us-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EI%20moved%20to%20the%20Netherlands%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20July%202024%2C%20I%20rented%20a%20typical%20Dutch%20terraced%20house%2C%20much%20bigger%20than%20I%20needed%2C%20on%20a%20one-year%20contract.%20As%20a%20self-employed%20therapist%2