%20wealth%20is%20swelling%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-many-billionaires-world-growing-net-worth-ai-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eranks%20of%20billionaires%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20with%20them%20comes%20a%20growing%20appetite%20for%20a%20favorite%20status%20symbol%3A%20superyachts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESales%20of%20preowned%20superyachts%20%E2%80%94%20which%20make%20up%20the%20majority%20of%20those%20sold%20%E2%80%94%20reached%20%246.4%20billion%20in%202025%2C%20up%2036%25%20from%202024%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20report%20by%20yacht%20brokerage%20Fraser%20Yachts.%20The%20number%20of%20new%20superyachts%2C%20those%20measuring%20over%2030%20meters%20in%20length%2C%20sold%20increased%206%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELong%20the%20domain%20of%20retirees%20and%20empty%20nesters%2C%20super%20yachting%20is%20attracting%20a%20younger%20crowd%2C%20hailing%20from%20industries%20like%20tech%2C%20and%20with%20their%20families%20in%20tow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20this%20trajectory%20where%20you%20grew%20into%20large%20yacht%20ownership%20through%20a%20succession%20of%20smaller%20yachts%2C%20and%20now%20we%20see%20people%20leapfrogging%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fday-in-the-life-superyacht-ceo-anders-kurten-monaco-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAnders%20Kurt%C3%A9n%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Fraser%20Yachts%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20uncommon%20today%20that%20somebody%20who's%20in%20their%2040s%20buying%20their%20first%20yacht%20goes%20directly%20to%20a%2050%20or%2060%20meter%20yacht.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYounger%20buyers%20have%20different%20priorities.%20They%20want%20bigger%20yachts%20%E2%80%94%20the%20number%20of%20new%20yachts%20over%2080%20meters%20increased%20from%2013%20to%2019%20last%20year%20%E2%80%94%20that%20are%20more%20sustainable%20and%20technologically%20advanced.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20want%20a%20seamless%20continuation%20of%20their%20on-shore%20lifestyle%20onboard%2C%26quot%3B%20Kurt%C3%A9n%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20includes%20entertainment%20for%20the%20kids%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20that%20comes%20in%20the%20form%20of%20waterslides%20and%20wakeboards%20or%20an%20on-board%20cinema%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20WFY%20%E2%80%94%20work%20from%20yacht.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20can%20run%20a%20board%20meeting%20for%20a%20publicly%20listed%20company%20from%20the%20conference%20room%20on%20your%20yacht%2C%26quot%3B%20Kurt%C3%A9n%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20priciest%20superyacht%20of%20the%20year%2C%20named%20Breakthrough%2C%20underscores%20the%20market's%20shift.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESold%20in%20September%20with%20a%20last%20asking%20price%20of%20%24793%20million%2C%20the%20superyacht%20measures%20119%20meters%20and%20is%20available%20to%20charter%20at%20a%20starting%20price%20of%20%244%20million%20a%20week.%20It%20boasts%20luxury%20features%20such%20as%20a%20tennis%20court%2C%20a%20helipad%2C%20and%20an%20infinity%20pool%2C%20as%20well%20as%20toys%2C%20including%20waterskis%2C%20inflatable%20kayaks%2C%20and%20paddle%20boards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pi%C3%A8ce%20de%20r%C3%A9sistance%20of%20Breakthrough's%20design%20lies%20in%20its%20engineering.%20It's%20the%20first%20superyacht%20powered%20by%20hydrogen%20fuel%20cells%2C%20meaning%20it%20can%20cruise%20emission-free.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20proportion%20of%20those%20for%20whom%20it%20is%20actually%20important%20is%20increasing%2C%26quot%3B%20Kurt%C3%A9n%20said%20of%20owners'%20views%20around%20sustainability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20priorities%20may%20shift%2C%20superyacht%20demand%20shows%20no%20signs%20of%20slowing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20global%20ultrawealthy%20population%20is%20expected%20to%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eincrease%20by%2031%25%20between%202025%20and%202030%2C%20according%20to%20the%202025%20World%20Ultra%20Wealth%20Report%20from%20wealth%20intelligence%20firm%20Altra