e%20work%20since%20Booz%20Allen%20Hamilton%20laid%20him%20off%20in%20August.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20he's%20cashed%20out%20his%20401(k)%20and%20collected%20unemployment%20to%20pay%20down%20debt%20and%20cover%20expenses.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ELaniewicz%20shared%20the%20job-hunting%20lessons%20he's%20learned%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Aaron%20Laniewicz%2C%20a%2040-year-old%20job%20seeker%20who%20lives%20in%20North%20Carolina.%20The%20following%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20getting%20laid%20off%2C%20I%20worked%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftreasury-department-cancel-contracts-booz-allen-hamilton-tax-return-leak-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBooz%20Allen%20Hamilton%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20a%20digital%20transformation%20consultant%20supporting%20government%20contracts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20my%20team%20began%20shrinking%20as%20our%20project%20got%20closer%20to%20completion%2C%20and%20I%20was%20eventually%20taken%20off%20the%20project%20and%20put%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-people-dont-understand-about-consulting-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20the%20bench%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%20Which%2C%20in%20consulting%2C%20means%20I%20was%20no%20longer%20assigned%20to%20a%20billable%20project%20and%20needed%20to%20find%20a%20new%20role%20internally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20looking%20right%20away%2C%20but%20with%20shifts%20in%20government%20spending%2C%20including%20efforts%20tied%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdoge-consulting-crackdown-what-contracts-are-being-cut-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EDepartment%20of%20Government%20Efficiency%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20our%20government%20contracts%20dried%20up.%20It%20was%20harder%20to%20find%20new%20consulting%20project