0I%20had%20been%20with%20the%20company%2C%20which%20amounted%20to%20about%20a%20month%20of%20severance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20collected%20unemployment%20benefits%2C%20but%20North%20Carolina%20%E2%80%94%20where%20I%20live%20and%20worked%20remotely%20%E2%80%94%20has%20one%20of%20the%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eleast%20generous%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Funemployment-benefits-versus-average-wages-across-the-us-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunemployment%20systems%20in%20the%20US%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20maximum%20payout%20is%20%244%2C200%2C%20and%20the%20most%20you%20can%20receive%20is%20%24350%20a%20week.%20My%20benefits%20didn't%20run%20out%2C%20but%20I%20had%20some%20freelance%20work%2C%20which%20disqualified%20me%20from%20receiving%20them.%20My%20last%20payment%20was%20the%20first%20week%20of%20December.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f06b1a14-e760-45a3-b40f-4f4933bc058f%5C%22%3EWe%20had%20to%20cash%20out%20my%20401(k)%20to%20get%20by%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20decided%20to%20liquidate%20my%20401(k)%2C%20which%20amounted%20to%20about%20%2450%2C000%2C%20and%20use%20it%20to%20pay%20down%20higher-interest%20debt%2C%20much%20of%20it%20credit%20card%20debt.%20It%20wasn't%20ideal%2C%20but%20the%20interest%20we%20were%20paying%20on%20our%20debt%20was%20higher%20than%20what%20we'd%20earn%20by%20keeping%20that%20money%20in%20savings%2C%20so%20it%20made%20more%20sense%20to%20take%20the%20hit%20of%20withdrawing%20it%20early.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20our%20finances%20are%20trending%20in%20an%20unsustainable%20direction.%20I've%20picked%20up%20some%20part-time%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efreelance%20work%20through%20a%20friend%20of%20a%20friend%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20a%20full-time%20replacement%20for%20the%20low-six-figure%20income%20I%20was%20making%20at%20Booz%20Allen.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a7601a90-a3f8-4ade-a97d-d80321c06e74%5C%22%3EI've%20focused%20on%20local%20opportunities%20to%20limit%20the%20competition%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20job%20search%20has%20gone%20through%20several%20stages.%20I've%20focused%20on%20roles%20centered%20on%20process%20management%2C%20automation%2C%20and%20data%20analysis%2C%20including%20ones%20where%20my%20experience%20with%20Power%20BI%2C%20a%20data%20visualization%20and%20reporting%20tool%2C%20would%20be%20valuable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarly%20on%2C%20there%20were%20a%20few%20promising%20opportunities%2C%20but%20they%20didn't%20work%20out%20because%20not%20being%20able%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmother-return-to-the-office-commute-childcare-nightmare-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ego%20into%20the%20office%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20a%20dealbreaker.%20That's%20part%20of%20why%20I%20started%20focusing%20on%20local%20opportunities.%20When%20I'm%20competing%20against%20people%20across%20the%20country%20for%20a%20remote%20position%2C%20the%20applicant%20pool%20is%20often%20much%20larger%20than%20for%20roles%20that%20require%20a%20local%20presence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdatawrapper.dwcdn.net%2Fg5mgr%2F1%2F%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Share%20of%20unemployed%20who%20are%20long-term%20unemployed%5C%22%20data-external%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22467%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20also%20started%20applying%20directly%20through%20company%20websites%20whenever%20possible.%20I%20noticed%20that%20on%20LinkedIn%2C%20there%20are%20sometimes%20multiple%20recruiters%20posting%20for%20the%20same%20job%2C%20without%20disclosing%20the%20company%20they%20are%20hiring%20for.%20I'd%20go%20through%20the%20application%20process%20and%20only%20later%20realize%20I'd%20already%20applied%20for%20the%20role%20%E2%80%94%20either%20directly%20or%20through%20another%20firm.%20It%20was%20a%20huge%20waste%20of%20time.%3C%2F