heir%20price%2C%20a%20former%20UK%20Royal%20Air%20Force%20official%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20go%20for%20mass%20because%20it's%20cheap%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20It%20enables%20mass%2C%20which%20produces%20operational%20effects.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-did-russia-invade-ukraine-putin-politics-motive-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efight%20against%20Russia's%20invasion%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20shown%20Western%20militaries%20the%20value%20of%20cheap%20weaponry%20in%20a%20large-scale%20conflict%2C%20and%20the%20advantages%20go%20beyond%20cost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECheap%20weapons%20matter%20because%20they%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthe-west-needs-more-cheap-weapons-counter-russia-and-china-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eenable%20mass%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20mass%20allows%20militaries%20to%20absorb%20losses%2C%20overwhelm%20defenses%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20go%20for%20mass%20because%20it's%20cheap%2C%26quot%3B%20retired%20Air%20Marshal%20Greg%20Bagwell%2C%20who%20spent%2036%20years%20in%20the%20British%20Royal%20Air%20Force%20and%20served%20as%20its%20joint%20warfare%20director%2C%20said.%20The%20cheaper%20it%20is%2C%20the%20better%2C%20he%20said%2C%20but%20the%20appeal%20of%20massed%20weaponry%20%26quot%3Bis%20not%20just%20because%20they're%20cheap.%26quot%3B%20There%20are%20operational%20effects.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMass%20allows%20for%20failures%2C%20losses%2C%20and%20ineffective%20outcomes.%20Think%20cheap%20quadcopter%20drones%20like%20Ukraine%20is%20using%20to%20target%20troops%20and%20tanks.%20Many%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwest-drone-training-sees-crashes-losses-part-process-learn-ukraine-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Enever%20reach%20their%20target%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECheap%20weaponry%20is%20often%20less%20effective%2C%20meaning%20more%20is%20necessary%20to%20get%20the%20job%20done%2C%20though%20it%20is%20still%20significantly%20cheaper%20than%20some%20higher-end%20capabilities.%20Thousands%20of%20these%20weapons%20can%20be%20acquired%20for%20the%20cost%20of%20only%20a%20handful%20of%20exquisite%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20real%20value%20of%20that%20mass%20of%20low-cost%20weaponry%20is%20that%20it%20allows%20militaries%20to%20overwhelm%20enemy%20defenses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20need%20to%20throw%20enough%20that%20you%20shut%20down%20their%20system%20and%20then%20exploit%20that%20gap%2C%26quot%3B%20Bagwell%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%227823%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20man%20in%20green%20gear%20holds%20a%20large%20grey%20drone%20over%20his%20shoulder%20as%20he%20walks%20through%20a%20green%20field%20with%20leaves%20in%20the%20foreground.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F697b53afd3c7faef0ecd271d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225282%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAllies%20are%20learning%20lessons%20in%20drone%20warfare%20from%20watching%20how%20key%20they%20are%20in%20Ukraine.%3Cp%3EGENYA%20SAVILOV%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMilitaries%20have%20to%20balance%20cost%2C%20volume%2C%20and%20effectiveness.%20%26quot%3BThe%20calculation%20is%20one%20that%20we're%20going%20to%20have%20to%20continually%20look%20at%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20decades%2C%20the%20West%20has%20heavily%20prioritized%20smaller%20quantities%20of%20advanced%20but%20expensive%20systems%20built%20for%20precision%2C%20not%20mass.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Ukraine's%20experience%20against%20Russia%20has%20forced%20a%20rethink.%20In%20this%20conflict%2C%20both%20nations%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fanalysis-putins-ukraine-attrition-plan-seems-to-be-working-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echewing%20through%20weapon%20inventories%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20fight%20that's%20defined%20by%20extensive%20use%20of%20cheaper%20weaponry%20like%20drones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia's%20war%20against%20Ukraine%20has%20pushed%20Western%20militaries%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnatos-focus-air-defenses-needed-from-way-russia-fighting-ukraine-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eboost%20their%20defense%20spending%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETroels%20Lund%20Poulsen%2C%20the%20Danish%20defense%20minister%2C%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20%26quot%3Bone%20of%20the%20lessons%26quot%3B%20from%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine%20was%20that%20the%20West%20needed%20far%20greater%20quantities%20of%20low-cost%20weaponry%20to%20meet%20the%20demands%20of%20a%20large-scale%2C%20high-intensity%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EUkraine's%20defense%20industry%20leaders%20are%20making%20similar%20observations%20from%20their%20country's%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESerhiy%20Goncharov%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20the%20National%20Association%20of%20Ukrainian%20Defense%20Industries%20%E2%80%94%20which%20represents%20about%20100%20Ukrainian%20companies%20%E2%80%94%20previously%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20West's%20longtime%20focus%20on%20a%20smaller%20number%20of%20exquisite%20systems%20would%20be%20the%20wrong%20approach%20if%20it%20were%20to%20find%20itself%20in%20a%20protracted%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20need%2010%20Archers%20from%20the%20Swedish%20that%20are%20probably%20one%20of%20the%20best%20artillery%20systems%20in%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20%3Cu%3Ethe%20artillery%20system%20made%3C%2Fu%3E%20by%20BAE%20Systems%20that%20Sweden%20gave%20to%20Ukraine.%20Instead%2C%20you%20need%20200%20cheap%20howitzers%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Bohdana%20one%20that%20Ukraine%20makes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fadvantage-cheap-weapons-modern-war-not-just-their-price-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3