%20in%20Uttarakhand%2C%20nestled%20in%20the%20Shivalik%20foothills%2C%20overlooking%20the%20stunning%20Raghati%20river.%20At%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F337165%2Fstartup-leopard-tech-lab-helps-kerala-forest-department-combat-wildlife-crime%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERajaji%20Raghati%20biosphere%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20all%20you%20need%20to%20do%20is%20sit%20on%20a%20rock%20and%20watch%20as%20leopards%2C%20elephants%2C%20and%20leopards%20pass%20by%2C%20while%20the%20air%20is%20filled%20with%20the%20sounds%20of%20chirping%20birds%20and%20buzzing%20insects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A498044%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Ftbi-showcase%2F%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fad-banner-1756106894.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESounds%20idyllic%2C%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20it%3F%20This%2032-acre%20biosphere%2C%20located%20within%20Rajaji%20National%20Park%20in%20Uttarakhand%2C%20is%20the%20brainchild%20of%20Jai%2C%20a%2052-year-old%20environmentalist%20and%20entrepreneur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInspired%20by%20the%20movie%20%3Cem%3EAvatar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Jai%20dreamed%20of%20living%20in%20a%20place%20like%20Pandora.%20For%20his%2050th%20birthday%2C%20he%20turned%20that%20dream%20into%20reality%20%E2%80%94%20not%20on%20a%20distant%20moon%2C%20but%20just%20four%20hours%20from%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJai%E2%80%99s%20vision%20for%20the%20biosphere%20in%20India%20was%20ambitious%3A%20to%20create%20a%20thriving%2C%20self-sustaini