to%20timeless%20art.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Srimoyee%20Chowdhury%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F496018%2Fcrochet-varmalas-indian-weddings-sustainable-ananya-malhotra-manya-jain-trending-garlands%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22As%20Floods%20Ravage%20Punjab%2C%203.5%20Lakh%20Struggle%20To%20Survive.%20Be%20Their%20Lifeline%2C%20Donate%20Today%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFarmer%20Mohan%20Singh%20was%20preparing%20to%20harvest%20the%20%3Cem%3Ekharif%20%3C%2Fem%3Ecrops%20on%20his%20field%20this%20week.%20He%20was%20elated%3B%20it%20had%20been%20a%20great%20season.%20So%20picture%20his%20devastation%20when%20he%20walked%20out%20onto%20his%20field%20three%20days%20ago%2C%20and%20saw%20that%20the%20green%20had%20been%20replaced%20by%20steadily%20rising%20water.%20Mohan%20belongs%20to%20Gurdaspur%20in%20Punjab%2C%20which%20is%20inundated%20by%20the%20waters%20flooding%20the%20state.%20The%20relentless%20heavy%20rains%20are%20compounded%20by%20the%20dangerously%20high%20levels%20of%20the%20Sutlej%2C%20Beas%2C%20and%20Ravi%20rivers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPunjab%20is%20drowning.%20It%20needs%20your%20help.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.donatekart.com%2FDisaster-Relief%2FThe-Better-India%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Clabel%3EDONATE%20NOW%20%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDonate%20to%20help%20Punjab%20flood%20victims%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmer%20Mohan%2C%20like%20the%203%2C54%2C000%20people%20(as%20of%205%20September)%20affected%2C%20did%20not%20have%20time%20to%20grieve.%20His%20only%20priority%20was%20ensuring%20that%20his%20family%20made%20it%20out%20of%20the%20house%20alive.%20But%20there%20was%20no%20escape%3B%20the%20only%20option%20was%20to%20wait%20and%20pray.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A496899%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Ftbi-showcase%2F%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fad-banner-1756106894.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%2C%20they%20saw%20a%20boat%20making%20its%20way%20to%20them.%20In%20it%20was%20Simranjit%20Singh%2C%20part%20of%20the%20Akal%20Relief%20Team%20at%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F391684%2Fcol-dr-rajinder-singh-started-akal-drug-de-addiction-centre-punjab-substance-abuse-alcoholism%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPunjab-based%20NGO%20Kalgidhar%20Trust%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20one%20of%20the%20many%20conducting%20relief%20and%20rescue%20operations%20on%20the%20ground%20supported%20by%20Donatekart.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20possibility%20of%20salvaging%20the%20house%20or%20any%20of%20the%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20belongings.%20But%20as%20they%20journeyed%20on%20the%20boat%20to%20the%20relief%20camp%20in%20Gurdaspur%2C%20Mohan%20broke%20down%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20fields%20are%20gone.%20I%20know%20I%20might%20not%20be%20able%20to%20sow%20anything%20for%20another%20year%20until%20the%20soil%20becomes%20fertile%20again%20and%20the%20mud%20is%20removed.%20What%20am%20I%20going%20to%20do%3F%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%